tps://youtu.be/2ChhN_jlMHE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2ChhN_jlMHE&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3RTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=4ef23d2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2ChhN_jlMHE</a><br />\n（主線任）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人建議可以睇曬劉細良呢兩日分析，對日後行動都有一個清晰嘅方向<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，<br />\n<br />\n第一段講現時政府架構變相成為軍政府，其次地區撥款已經接近被中聯辦完全操控。中共撥落香港嘅維穩費用唔係無限大，換言之就係用香港人嘅錢養住一班港共。<br />\n<br />\n第二段就係群眾利用消費者力量統一戰線，從而制衡紅色資本。（近日寶礦力例子）<br />\n<br />\n我覺得要將日常生活嘅細節串聯一齊，令大多數人知道港共嘅禍害，先可以打正旗號郁中聯辦。"},{"pid":"535574a909312dd364283ac8587585cf018e821e","tid":1304112,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbe4699332f8335b04c07dfd1f44d32904734aa8","tid":1304112,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5c7591e1a1d71e43eb825d550080c8d8941dba","tid":1304112,"uid":260161,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"咁打大佬都要練下等先啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"連儂牆有咩練？"},{"pid":"08b7c47e89e6de7ce86f9fcb021f51a4febdb894","tid":1304112,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8e498b2b84a32e4f448f5958f37b73655dd9177","tid":1304112,"uid":34120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbe4699332f8335b04c07dfd1f44d32904734aa8","tid":1304112,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5c7591e1a1d71e43eb825d550080c8d8941dba","tid":1304112,"uid":260161,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"咁打大佬都要練下等先啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"連儂牆有咩練？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"連儂牆令到多人關注係好事，但連儂牆呢個只係屬於送信任，唔需要刻意做。<br />\n<br />\n假設每個地區都有連儂牆，到時出任嘅成本就會降低好多。連儂牆嘅作用就唔單止係引起關注，更可以係戰略訊息中心。"},{"p